{"tid":1292273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.7 九龍大遊行】英國遊客參與遊行　撐港人爭取民主","createTime":"2019-07-07T08:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T09:36:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8162604fd98136c1eb07981251d747ef20f17e","tid":1292273,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202019-07-0720at204.19.2720PM_osLwQ_1200x0_66UBP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202019-07-0720at204.19.2720PM_osLwQ_1200x0_66UBP_1200x0.png&h=8ec3e7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有團體今日將發起「九龍區大遊行」活動，由尖沙咀梳士巴利公園前往高鐵西九龍站，遊行隊伍中包括外籍遊行的身影。有來自英國的遊客現身遊行現場，表明支持所以爭取民主的人，獲其他遊行人士致謝。<br />\n<br />\n三名來自英國的遊客手持標語，支持遊行人士。他們由英國前來，剛巧停留香港一天，之後將轉飛至星加坡旅行。他們表示，今日是特意到尖沙咀支持遊行人士。其中一名遊客Chris指，他們支持所以爭取民主的人。  對於英方政府數次針對香港現時情況的發言，他們指，他們明白政府一方面不想破壞與中國的關係，另一方面他們仍會極力關注香港現時情況。不少遊行人士在隊伍中感謝他們。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/7-7-九龍大遊行-英國遊客參與遊行-撐港人爭取民主/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-7-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%92%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=1bd21c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-7-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%92%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&h=5d5d56a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/7-7-九龍大遊行-英國遊客參與遊行-撐港人爭取民主/</a>"},{"pid":"e172799db05da453f3e439d680f76ba81054dcde","tid":1292273,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"【